greeting: Greetings from The On-Line Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences! http://oeis.org/

results.name: Decimal expansion of 180*(1 - arctan(2)/Pi).
comment: Dihedral angle in degrees of regular dodecahedron.
program: (PARI) default(realprecision, 105); x=18/10*(1-atan(2)/Pi); for(n=1, 105, d=floor(x); x=(x-d)*10; print1(d, ", "));
results.author: _Arkadiusz Wesolowski_, May 21 2014
